summary:
About Us - Once upon a time, in the shadowy depths of the murky pond, King Pauly made a bold decision to wage war against NikiChain, disputing the human ethics of the crypto industry. Amidst fierce battles and many fallen comrades, King Pauly emerged triumphant, with NikiChain humbly surrendering. Now, the next chapter unfolds as our noble king endeavors to reunite with his queen, who awaits to whisk him away to the Cheesecake Factory in faraway land. Be sure to keep your ears attuned for our forthcoming adventure, set to debut in July 2024, where you can embark on daring missions and aid the Pond Queen in her journey to be reunited with her beloved King so they can rule their Pond Kingdom together and make the world a better place.
